OL,3,CManslaughter charge following attack
OL,4,C13 years ago
OL,6,FA 40-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith manslaughter after a man died 10
OL,8,Fyears after being attacked in Swindon.
OL,10,FSam Rees was 27 when he was assaulted
OL,11,Fin Old Town, on 1 April 2013. He
OL,12,Fsustained serious head injuries in the
OL,13,Fattack and died a decade later in
OL,14,FDecember 2023.
OL,16,FFollowing Mr Rees' death, Wiltshire
OL,17,FPolice reopened the investigation into
OL,18,Fthe assault.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
