OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777306270
OL,3,CManslaughter charge following attack
OL,4,C13 years ago
OL,6,FAbuzer Erdam, of Ferndale Road, in
OL,7,FSwindon, has now been charged with his
OL,8,Fmanslaughter.
OL,10,FHe has been released on conditional
OL,11,Fbail and is due to appear at Swindon
OL,12,FMagistrates Court on 26 May.
OL,14,FDet Con Jemma Humphreys, of the Major
OL,15,FCrime Investigation Team, said: "This
OL,16,Fis a tragic case of a young man who
OL,17,Fsuffered significant injuries
OL,18,Ffollowing an assault in Swindon and
OL,19,Ftragically died 10 years later.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
