OL,3,CManslaughter charge following attack
OL,4,C13 years ago
OL,6,F"I'd like to take this opportunity to
OL,7,Fremind the public of the dangers of
OL,8,Fnight-time economy-fuelled violence.
OL,10,F"Please consider the consequences of
OL,11,Fyour actions, and always stop, think
OL,12,Fand walk away."
